item.title: CVE-2023-49897|2023-12-22T04:06:04.193Z -- fxc%20inc. -- ae1021pe
item.description: An OS command injection vulnerability exists in AE1021PE firmware version 2.0.9 and earlier and AE1021 firmware version 2.0.9 and earlier. If this vulnerability is exploited, an arbitrary OS command may be executed by an attacker who can log in to the product.
